I '''Ian Lancaster Fleming''' (28 Mayo 1908&nbsp;– 12 Agosto 1964) metung yang Ingles a talasulat, peryodista ampong [[Naval Intelligence Division|naval intelligence officer]], a kilalang dili ketang kayang serie da reng nobelang ispiyang [[James Bond]]. series of [[spy novel]]s. Ibat ya i Fleming king makwaltang pamilyang maki kaugnayan king bangkung pangkomersyung (''merchant bank'') [[Robert Fleming & Co.]], at Myembru ne ning Parlamento i tata nang pekakatawan ning [[Henley (UK Parliament constituency)|Henley]] manibat 1910 angga king kayang kamatayan king  [[Western Front (World War I)|Western Front]] anyang 1917. Megaral ya king [[Eton College|Eton]], [[Royal Military Academy Sandhurst|Sandhurst]] ampo deng unibersidad ning [[Munich University|Munich]] ampong [[University of Geneva|Geneva]], i Fleming, a dinalan kareng mapilang obra bayu ya migumpisang sumulat.  

Kabang magobra ya king 
British naval intelligence anyang [[Kadwang Gerang Pangyatu]], miugne ya i Fleming king pamagplanu ning [[Operation Mincemeat]] ampo ning [[Operation Golden Eye]]. Miugne ya mu naman king pamagplanu ampong pamaglawe He was also involved in the planning and (''oversight'') da reng adwang ''intelligence unit'', ing [[30 Assault Unit]] ampo ing [[T-Force]]. Ibat king kayang serbisyu ampo karera antimong peryodista ing minye "kagulutan" ("background"), detalye ampong lalam kareng nobelang James Bond.  

Sinulat neng Fleming ing mumuna nang nobela, ing ''[[Casino Royale (nobela)|Casino Royale]]'', anyang 1952.  Metung yang tagumpe, a mekatatlu milimbag It was a success, with (''three print runs'') a mekumisyun bang pakibatan ing pamangaylangan kaniti. Labi lang metung deng nobela ampong koleksyon da reng makuyad a salitang  being commissioned to cope with the demand.  Eleven Bond novels and two {''short-story collections'') tinuki kaniti, pilatan ning 1953 ampong 1966. Dudurut la reng nobela kang [[James Bond (tauan king literatura)|James Bond]], metung a opisyal king Secret Intelligence Service, a keraklan awsan dang [[Secret Intelligence Service|MI6]]. Mayayaus ya mu naman i Bond king kayang code number a 007, at [[Commander (Royal Navy)|commander]] ya king [[Royal Naval Reserve]].  Kayabe la reng kuwentung Bond kareng [[List of best-selling books#At least 100 million copies|pekamasaling librung piksyon]] king kabilugan ning panaun, uling misali no reng 100&nbsp;milyung kopya king mabilug a yatu.  Sinulat ne mu namang Fleming ing kuwentung pang-anák a ''[[Chitty-Chitty-Bang-Bang (nobela)|Chitty-Chitty-Bang-Bang]]'' ampong adwang obra ning e piksyon and two works of (''non-fiction''). Anyang 2008, binili ne ning ''[[The Times]]'' i Fleming king ranggung ka-labing apat (''fourteenth'') king kayang listaan da reng   "The 50 greatest [[British literature|British writers]] since 1945" (limampulung mapyang diling talasulat a Britaniko manibat anyang 1945).

Asawa ne i Ann Charteris, a midiborsyu king kadwang Viscount Rothermere uli ning kayang pamakiugnayan kang Fleming. Atin lang anak di Fleming ampong Charteris, i Caspar. Matalik yang sindi ampong minum i Fleming, a maki sakit king pusu; mete ya anyang 1964 king idad a 56, king ataki king pusu. Adwa la reng librung James Bond a milimbag kaybat nang mete, at bukud kaniti, lima lang aliwa pang talasulat deng ginawang nobelang Bond. Adwang pulu't apat neng ukdu o besis mipalage kareng pelikula ing tauan nang Fleming, at pitu lang artista deng linage kaniti. 
